    "text": "Recently, I got invited by Pavlina F. to the Junior Guru podcast, focused on juniors in IT.\nIn this episode, we addressed:\n\n🎙️ academic & industrial careers\n🎙️ how to start in IT from scratch\n🎙️ the formal education and whether it is needed\n🎙️ future of programming in the age of AI\n🎙️ my experience with hiring juniors\n\nYou can find the podcast here:\nhttps://lnkd.in/eBAs2_-u\nor here: https://lnkd.in/e7yTAAxE\n\n🇨🇿 The podcast is in Czech 🇨🇿 but I’m happy to discuss all these topics and how we tackle them in Deloitte also in English.\nThanks for having me 🙏 \n\n#podcast #AI #genAI #IT",
